# V8 package

- Target: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
- V8 version: @V8_VERSION@
- LLVM toolchain: @LLVM_VERSION@
- Upstream checkout: https://chromium.googlesource.com/v8/v8

This package contains V8 public headers, shared V8 component libraries, the
`d8` shell, pkg-config metadata, and CMake discovery metadata. It is intended
as an input for PostgreSQL PL/V8 builds.

The package is built through the official `depot_tools`/`fetch v8`/GN/Ninja
flow with `is_component_build=true`, `v8_enable_i18n_support=false`, and
`v8_use_external_startup_data=false`.
